t: Overland quit Amazon. Can other luxury succeed? | Vogue Business
s: October 21, 2020 - This August, a $165 cowhide backpack called the Odessa sold on Amazon and shipped to a customer in Lakeville, Massachusetts. It was the final Amazon sale from the Overland Sheepskin Co., an American heritage brand and purveyor of sheepskin, leather and fur apparel.
